Tickle Tunes Part 3 (04/13/2026)

Players roll a d20 dice to determine playing order. The player with the highest roll is the first Guesser. The DJ is selected randomly by spin the bottle.

The Guesser selects an artist and has to guess a song from that artist provided by the DJ.
    *Once a artist is choosen, it cannot be used again this phase.

If the Guesser, guesses correctly then they choose another artist, and play again with a different DJ. This continues until the guesser fails. Then the next player repears until all players have played.
    *The DJ drinks for every correct guess!

Winner is derermined by the player who gains the most points during the phase!

